    No billable hours. No change orders. No project that runs 3x over budget and
    delivers half the scope.
  </p>

  <p class="lede">
    But the automations are just the beginning. What you're really building is
    your firm's token capital &mdash; a compounding institutional asset. We
    architect systems where you can swap the underlying model without losing the
