  </p>

  <p class="cta-block">
    <a class="cta" href="mailto:engage@primorum.ai?subject=Free%20AI%20Operations%20Audit">Request your free audit &rarr;</a>
    <span class="cta-note">30 minutes. Zero cost. One concrete report.</span>
  </p>
